      <p>PestControlNearMe provides professional pest control and pest management services for residential, commercial, and industrial properties across India. Services include but are not limited to cockroach control, termite treatment, mosquito control, rodent management, bed bug treatment, and general pest control.</p>

      <h2>2. Service Guarantee</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We provide a <strong>3-month service guarantee</strong> on all standard pest control treatments.</li>
        <li>If pests reappear within the guarantee period, we will re-treat the affected area at no additional cost.</li>
        <li>The guarantee is valid only if the customer follows the post-treatment care instructions provided by our technician.</li>
        <li>The guarantee does not cover new infestations from external sources or untreated areas.</li>
